To build and run this image download the db (https://sites.google.com/site/bioericscript/download) and move the homo_sapiens folder in the current directory.

Then install inside a new sample folder the sample files:

$ mkdir sample
$ cd sample
$ fastq-dump --split-files <ID_file>

(ID_file example: SRR064286)

Build the image, then run:
$ sudo docker run ericscript